This paper deals with XML data warehouses and OLAP analyses over XML data cubes, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses XQuery extensions, which are relevant to web technologies (cs.WEB). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algebra for expressing OLAP operators, which could be of interest to researchers in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and digital libraries (cs.DL) who work with data analysis and information retrieval.
